Privacy Policy for Page Note

Last updated: April 27, 2026

Page Note does not collect, store, transmit, or share any personal data.

All notes created by the user are stored locally in the browser using 
Chrome's built-in storage API (chrome.storage.local). This data never 
leaves the user's device and is not accessible to the developer or any 
third party.

The extension does not use analytics, tracking, or any external services.

